__NOTOC__ 
{{Client function}}
{{Added feature/item|1.5.9|1.5.8|20901|This function gets the amount of memory (in bytes) used by the GTA streamer.}}

==Syntax== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">int engineStreamingGetUsedMemory ( )</syntaxhighlight>

===Returns===
* Returns a [[int]] containing the amount of memory in bytes.

==Example==
This example gets the amount of memory used by the streamer when the resource starts:
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
addEventHandler ("onClientResourceStart", resourceRoot,
    function ()
        outputChatBox ("Used memory by the GTA streamer: "..engineStreamingGetUsedMemory ()..".")
    end
)
</syntaxhighlight>

==Requirements==
{{Requirements|n/a|1.5.8-9.20901|}}

